page.title: 03HOUSING
page.content: In our area there are many different sorts of housing and it is probably mostly residential land. The housing at{Keyham }is mostly residential land. When we get nearer the centre of town it starts to become industry. Housing in{Keyham}is mostly terraced,the houses are small with no front garden and a back yard and alley.Many small shops are amongst the houses.They are Edwardian or Victorian.Some houses in our area Many small shops are amongst the houses.They are Edwardian or Victorian.Some houses in our area are council houses.These houses are short terraced with gardens or semi-detached.There are some flats of four storeys but no high rise.
